      <a href="#" style="background:var(--surface-2);border:1px solid var(--steel-200);border-radius:8px;padding:24px;text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
        <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--steel-600);letter-spacing:0.08em;">DEEP DIVE</div>
        <h5 style="font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);line-height:1.35;margin-top:8px;margin-bottom:12px;">The role of CAPA Tracking in compliance and audit-readiness.</h5>
        <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--steel-600);">11 Apr 2026</div>
      </a>
      <a href="#" style="background:var(--surface-2);border:1px solid var(--steel-200);border-radius:8px;padding:24px;text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
        <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--steel-600);letter-spacing:0.08em;">PRACTICE</div>
        <h5 style="font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);line-height:1.35;margin-top:8px;margin-bottom:12px;">Safety audit vs safety inspection: what's the difference?</h5>
