  <div class="container">
    <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-end;margin-bottom:32px;">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">Industry insights</span>
        <h3 class="h1" style="margin-top:4px;">From the field</h3>
      </div>
      <a href="#" class="btn-tertiary arrow-right">All 19 insights</a>
    </div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:24px;">
      <a href="#" style="background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--steel-200);border-radius:8px;padding:28px;text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
        <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--pink);letter-spacing:0.08em;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:12px;">CONFERENCE</div>
        <h5 style="font-size:17px;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);line-height:1.3;margin-bottom:12px;">PSCI India: key insights from the floor.</h5>
        <p style="font-size:13.5px;color:var(--steel-700);line-height:1.5;">What's shifting in pharma supply-chain safety as global procurement standards tighten on Indian manufacturers.</p>
